{"tid":2283403,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Microsoft 已確認 Windows 10 20H2 存在隨機強制重啟與藍屏的問題","createTime":"2020-11-12T14:01:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-05T16:55:24.000Z","uid":1886,"like":17,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"f5c50a49dc5d443c4f4e2b508691a68991be1b14","tid":2283403,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:01:55.000Z","msg":"由 Windows 10 20H2 (十月更新) 推出以來，已有不少用戶反映大量 Bug。而在 20H2 發布短短兩星期後，Microsoft 就證實存在用戶登錄後會遇到藍屏或強制重啟警告。當時 Microsoft 在公佈中指：Windows 10 的功能更新導致了相容性和藍屏死機問題，並且附上了「DRIVER_VERIFIER_DMA_VIOLATION (e6)」的錯誤代碼。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/biOP8f1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbiOP8f1.jpg&h=9618b34e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在報錯訊息顯示「某個經過驗證的驅動程序，嘗試了一個非法的直接記憶體訪問 (DMA) 操作」。而 Microsoft 和 Intel 在檢查後發現，問題與某些 NVMe SSD 驅動的相容性有關。為避免影響擴大，Microsoft 已阻止這部分裝置的 Windows 10 更新。<br />\n<br />\n另外，Microsoft 亦確認了另一個錯誤，Windows 10 會隨機要求您登出並強制重啟電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，主要因存在這兩個功能：本地安全授權和 MMC 管理單元。<br />\n<br />\n若已出現上述問題，需要手動移除更新、並回復到早前的 Windows 版本。另外保險起見，亦可手動禁用 Windows 10 的自動更新，直到正式的解決方案推出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.xfastest.com/77427/windows-10-20h2-bugs/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.xfastest.com%2F77427%2Fwindows-10-20h2-bugs%2F&d=K%2BViKRLCts5CIle5BUc%2ByoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=027e8be1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.xfastest.com/77427/windows-10-20h2-bugs/</a>"},{"pid":"86482ef1567f8ab0f200496a1a9903e917469363","tid":2283403,"uid":81113,"like":9,"dislike":1,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T14:06:45.000Z","msg":":(<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbd35e2baa1e0f4ea445229b257f373e7820fc87","tid":2283403,"uid":263944,"like"